Field Label:
Earlier you told me you might do things that may get you into trouble with adults like breaking rules or getting into trouble with the police or other authorities. I am now going to ask you some questions about this. 


SYMPTOMS
Stayed Out Late
Did you ever get into trouble because you stayed out at night later than your parents permitted? (> 2 hours)
How old were you the first time you stayed out at night later than your parents permitted?
Has Run Away from Home Overnight
Did you ever run away from home overnight?
How many times?
How old were you the first time you ran away from home?
Stolen from Family
Did you ever secretly steal money or other things from your family or from the other people you live with?
Stolen without Confrontation
Did you ever shoplift or steal something from others or a store worth at least $5?
Often Lies
Did you often tell lies:
To trick people into giving you things?
To get people to do what you want them to do?
To get out of doing things you were supposed to do?
Often Truant from School
Did you often skip school?
How many times did you skip school?
How old were you the first time you skipped school?
Has Broken into Someone Else's Property
Did you ever break into a house, a building, or a car?
Has Deliberately Destroyed Others' Property
Did you ever deliberately damage someone else's property, by doing something like breaking windows, slashing tires, or writing on buildings?
How many times?
Deliberately Engaged in Fire Setting
Did you ever start a fire to try to cause serious damage?
Physically Cruel to Animals
Have you ever been physically cruel to an animal and hurt it on purpose?
Often Bullies Others
Did you often bully others? (Hitting, threatening or scaring someone who was younger or smaller)
Was this only with your brother or sister?
Deliberately Threatened/Frightened Someone
Did you threaten or frighten someone on purpose?
Was this only with your brother or sister?
Often Initiates Physical Fights
Did you often start physical fights with others?
Physically Cruel to People
Were you ever physically cruel to another person and hurt him or her on purpose?
Tried to Hurt Someon with a Weapon
Did you ever try to hurt someone with a weapon like a bat, brick, broken bottle, knife, or gun?
Stolen with Confrontation of a Victim
Did you ever threaten someone, hold someone up, or attack someone to steal from them?
Forced Someone into Sexual Activity
Did you ever trick or threaten someone into having sex with you?
Did anyone ever accuse you of making them do something sexual?

If yes, what happened?  
INTERVIEWER: Rate yes only if it sounds like they forced, manipulated, or threatened someone else into sexual activity.
INTERVIEWER: If no to all, END Conduct Disorder section.
